# Source Midjourney rolls and working images are kept locally for
# iteration but not committed — they're ~40MB and the firmware only
# consumes the canonical `state_*.png` files. If we settle on a roll
# we want versioned long-term, copy it to a state_*.png name; that
# pattern is the only one tracked.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!state_*.png
